"{\"uid\": \"blueprint.ng-nigerias-disastrous-paris-olympics-performance-continues-as-another-athlete-fails-to-win-weightlifting-medal\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"August 10, 2024Admin IIISports0 Team Nigeria's hope of a medal at the on-going Paris Olympic Games was all but dashed on Friday evening after weightlifter Joy Eze missed out on medals table.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 191, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 38, \"end\": 45, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.727809547187478e-41, \"text\": \"Nigeria\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\"}, {\"begin\": 156, \"end\": 163, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joy_Eze\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Joy Eze\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joy_Eze\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joy_Eze\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a medal\", \"from\": 55, \"to\": 62}, {\"ngram\": \"the on-going Paris Olympic Games\", \"from\": 66, \"to\": 98}, {\"ngram\": \"Friday evening\", \"from\": 121, \"to\": 135}, {\"ngram\": \"medals table\", \"from\": 177, \"to\": 189}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 2023 Africa Games champion went into the weightlifting event at the South Paris Arena hoping to out Nigeria's name on the medals table, though weightlifting enthusiasts believe that with proper and sustained training and exposure she will be the star to beat in in Los Angeles Olympic Games four years later.\", \"from\": 193, \"to\": 505, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 297, \"end\": 304, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.727809547187478e-41, \"text\": \"Nigeria\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\"}, {\"begin\": 462, \"end\": 487, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1984_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999951387908291, \"rank\": 4.8612328215840424e-06, \"text\": \"Los Angeles Olympic Games\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1984_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1984_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The 2023 Africa Games champion\", \"from\": 193, \"to\": 223}, {\"ngram\": \"the weightlifting event\", \"from\": 234, \"to\": 257}, {\"ngram\": \"the South Paris Arena\", \"from\": 261, \"to\": 282}, {\"ngram\": \"the medals table\", \"from\": 315, \"to\": 331}, {\"ngram\": \"weightlifting enthusiasts\", \"from\": 340, \"to\": 365}, {\"ngram\": \"proper and sustained training\", \"from\": 384, \"to\": 413}, {\"ngram\": \"exposure\", \"from\": 418, \"to\": 426}, {\"ngram\": \"the star\", \"from\": 439, \"to\": 447}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, her 101kg snatch and 131kh clean and jerk with a total of 231kg,were not enough to land her in the medals rank as she ended her campaign 7th.\", \"from\": 507, \"to\": 657, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her 101kg snatch\", \"from\": 516, \"to\": 532}, {\"ngram\": \"131kh clean\", \"from\": 537, \"to\": 548}, {\"ngram\": \"jerk\", \"from\": 553, \"to\": 557}, {\"ngram\": \"a total\", \"from\": 563, \"to\": 570}, {\"ngram\": \"231kg\", \"from\": 574, \"to\": 579}, {\"ngram\": \"the medals\", \"from\": 611, \"to\": 621}, {\"ngram\": \"her campaign 7th\", \"from\": 640, \"to\": 656}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Joy had hoped to make a record debut performance at the olympics USA's Olivia Reeves won gold, setting a new snatch Olympic record of 117kg.\", \"from\": 659, \"to\": 800, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 725, \"end\": 728, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999950584109908, \"rank\": 4.859296359956488e-06, \"text\": \"USA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 731, \"end\": 737, \"title\"